You are an expert full-stack engineer and Indian tax compliance specialist. Build a production-ready, multi-tenant SaaS application called "InvoiceOS" — a GST + Invoicing Autopilot for Indian MSMEs.

---

## PRODUCT OVERVIEW

InvoiceOS helps Indian small businesses (kirana shops, traders, D2C sellers) generate GST-compliant invoices, auto-file GSTR-1 and GSTR-3B returns, generate e-Invoices (IRN), reconcile GSTR-2A, and collect payments via UPI — all from one dashboard.

---

## TECH STACK

Frontend: Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
Backend: Node.js with tRPC (or REST as fallback), Prisma ORM
Database: PostgreSQL (via Supabase or Neon)
Auth: Clerk or NextAuth.js (multi-tenant, org-aware)
Queue: BullMQ + Redis (for GSTN API jobs)
Storage: AWS S3 or Cloudflare R2 (PDF invoices)
Payments: Razorpay (subscription billing + UPI payment links)
PDF: Puppeteer or @react-pdf/renderer
Email: Resend
Monitoring: Sentry + PostHog
Deployment: Vercel (frontend) + Railway or Render (backend workers)

