## CORE MODULES TO BUILD

### 1. Authentication & Multi-tenancy
- Org-level isolation (every DB query scoped by org_id)
- Invite teammates with role-based permissions
- CA portal: one CA user can manage multiple org accounts
- Subscription gating: enforce invoice limits on Starter plan

### 2. Invoice Engine
- Invoice creation form with:
  - Auto HSN/SAC code lookup (build a searchable table of ~20,000 codes)
  - Auto GST rate detection from HSN code
  - CGST/SGST vs IGST logic (intra-state vs inter-state based on place_of_supply)
  - Reverse charge toggle
  - Line-item level discount support
  - Invoice number auto-generation: ORG_PREFIX/FY/SEQ (e.g. TRD/24-25/001)
- PDF generation: professional A4 GST invoice PDF with QR code (for e-Invoice), org logo
- WhatsApp share: generate a wa.me link with PDF attachment via WhatsApp Business API
- UPI payment link: generate Razorpay payment link and embed in invoice PDF + email

### 3. e-Invoice (IRN) Generation
- Integrate with IRP sandbox first, then production
- Build the exact JSON schema per GST e-Invoice schema v1.1
- Fields: SupplierGSTIN, ReceiverGSTIN, DocDetails, ItemList, ValDtls, TaxDetails
- On submit: call IRP API → receive IRN + AckNo + signed QR
- Embed QR in PDF re-generation
- Handle errors: duplicate IRN, invalid GSTIN, schema validation failures
- Store all attempts with error logs

### 4. GSTN API Integration (GSP Route)
- Register as a GST Suvidha Provider (GSP) or use an existing GSP (Masters India, IRIS, Karvy GST)
- Implement OTP-based authentication (taxpayer GSTIN + OTP from GST portal)
- Build GSTR-1 JSON generator:
  - B2B invoices (b2b section)
  - B2C large invoices >₹2.5L (b2cl)
  - B2C small invoices (b2cs — state-wise summary)
  - Credit/debit notes (cdnr, cdnur)
  - Nil-rated, exempt, non-GST supplies (nil)
  - HSN summary (hsn)
- Build GSTR-3B calculator:
  - Auto-aggregate from invoice data
  - Outward taxable supplies by rate
  - ITC eligible vs ineligible
  - Net tax payable
- Filing flow: Draft → Review diff → Confirm → Submit to GSTN → Store ARN
- Handle filing window: GSTR-1 due 11th, GSTR-3B due 20th of following month
- Send reminder notifications (email + WhatsApp) 3 days before due date

### 5. GSTR-2A Reconciliation
- Fetch GSTR-2A data from GSTN API (supplier-filed invoices)
- Match against purchase invoices entered by user
- Show three-way reconciliation: Matched / In 2A not in books / In books not in 2A
- Flag ITC claims at risk

### 6. Tally Integration
- Parse Tally XML exports (Tally Prime / ERP9 format)
- Map Tally voucher types to InvoiceOS invoice model
- Two-way sync: push invoices back to Tally via Tally XML format
- Handle GSTIN validation, duplicate detection

### 7. Dashboard & Analytics
- MRR/revenue view for the business owner
- GST liability tracker: how much CGST/SGST/IGST is owed this month
- Outstanding receivables by customer
- Top customers by revenue
- Filing calendar: upcoming due dates with status

### 8. Subscription & Billing
- Razorpay Subscriptions for monthly recurring billing
- Plan enforcement middleware: check invoice count, GSTIN count, API access
- Usage-based alerts: "You've used 80% of your invoice quota"
- Upgrade prompts in-product

