## COMPLIANCE RULES TO IMPLEMENT

1. GSTIN validation: regex ^[0-9]{2}[A-Z]{5}[0-9]{4}[A-Z]{1}[1-9A-Z]{1}Z[0-9A-Z]{1}$ + checksum
2. HSN mandatory for turnover >₹5Cr (6 digits), optional below (4 digits)
3. e-Invoice mandatory for turnover >₹5Cr — auto-detect from org profile
4. IGST applies if supplier state != place_of_supply state; else CGST+SGST split equally
5. Reverse charge: flag specific HSN codes and unregistered vendor purchases
6. Invoice cancellation: only within 24 hours of IRN generation (IRP rule)
7. e-Way Bill: required if goods value >₹50,000 (Phase 3)

